Vim plugin: Tortf
================
To convert text to rtf format and paste to the system clipboard

Usage
-----
Select the target codes, then run :Tortf. That's it.

Limitation
----------
It's only tested in Mac, with the help of `textutil` and `pbcopy` commands. 

